{"tid":160989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海黑線鱈魚量急跌　英人無炸魚薯條食？","createTime":"2017-03-18T08:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T14:46:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c79b43f7240e1fb675c4cd5532fcbeb43bb6adb5","tid":160989,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"03月18日(六) 12:55   <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170318/bknint-20170318125529040-0318_17011_001.html?view=d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170318%2Fbknint-20170318125529040-0318_17011_001.html%3Fview%3Dd&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=d0de0072\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170318/bknint-20170318125529040-0318_17011_001.html?view=d</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170318/photo/bknint-20170318125529040-0318_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170318140438\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170318%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170318125529040-0318_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170318140438&h=1221b86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">黑線鱈魚（上）數量大跌，第時無炸魚薯條食？（資料圖片）</span><br />\n英國人愛吃炸魚薯條，其中一種最常用於炸魚中的黑線鱈魚，被英國海洋保諼協會在可持續食用種類名單中除名，原因是這種鱈魚的數量不斷下降，去年的數目低於建議的水平，需要採取行動加長牠們的飼養期。 <br />\n<br />\n協會指出，它們已將在北海及蘇格蘭西岸的黑線鱈魚，從可持續食用種類的「好魚指引」名單中除名，不再是可經常食用的魚類之列。黑線鱈是英國五大海產種類之一，和另一種鱈魚、俗稱吞那魚的金槍魚，以及三文魚和蝦，是英國人最常食用的海產。<br />\n<br />\n不過，蘇格蘭漁民聯合會表示，黑線鱈存量下降和存量審查一致，是拜科學家不幸的錯誤所造成。聯合會總裁批評海洋保諼協會的決定，呼籲公眾不用擔心海中是否仍有足夠魚類剩下來，繼續購買魚食。"},{"pid":"5a561ee903d7c0ad656a12c4fbde5566805fffa5","tid":160989,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f6979dc1b4dde202efb2f02483e780b552684d","tid":160989,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}